DC's first-ever virtual convention DC Fandome is in the books! With it, came a slew of teasers, news, announcements, and surprises for all your favorite DC properties. In this episode The Don and Yogi geek out over some of the cooler teases while raising eyebrows about other goings-on in the industry. Join us as we try to predict the plot of The Batman, debate The Snyder Cut and try to guess who's gonna die in James Gunn's The Suicide Squad! Please leave us a review on [ITunes](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our [merchandise](http://www.teepublic.com/user/comicbookclique)! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by [ComicBookClique.com](../episode/update/id/Comicbokclique.com), the home for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media. Send us feedback at ComicBookClique@Gmail.com! You Are Worthy! 

